but in this case,

607
00:35:29.440 --> 00:35:33.120
in vitro imaging modalities is what is meant by imaging,

608
00:35:33.600 --> 00:35:37.140
not clinical radiology. So clinical radiology is not

609
00:35:37.220 --> 00:35:40.920
applicable for this type of funding opportunity.

610
00:35:42.160 --> 00:35:45.530
The first phase, or the phase of analytical validity,

611
00:35:45.720 --> 00:35:49.520
refers to how reliable the measurement is for

612
00:35:49.600 --> 00:35:53.280
