614
00:35:57.300 --> 00:36:01.240
precision, sensitivity, and specificity.

615
00:36:01.300 --> 00:36:05.000
And the second phase, the phase of analytical validity, refers

616
00:36:05.140 --> 00:36:09.040
to how reproducible the association is between the measurement

617
00:36:09.100 --> 00:36:11.340
and the clinical outcome of interest.

618
00:36:13.200 --> 00:36:13.540
